overview.en: I come (wolai.cc) is a vertical community of problem-solvers in the field of token-driven software. When I come, the user's contribution and contribution will receive a corresponding return. UBQ is the blockchain token I came from, which represents the right to use me and its surrounding ecology.
overview.zh: 我来（wolai.cc）是代币驱动的软件领域问题解答者垂直社区。在我来，用户的付出和贡献将获得相应的回报。UBQ 是我来的区块链代币，代表我来及其周边生态的使用权。
